    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for your next dream ride? Because this beauty is an absolute showstopper! I have meticulously cared for this car, and it is in truly mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no stories, just a perfect ride ready for a new home. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
