    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, showroom-quality 2021 BMW M3 Competition in Isle of Man Green. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents as though it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior features a full-body ceramic coating with zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections in the paintwork. Inside, the Kyalami Orange Extended Merino Leather remains taut and supple, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma; the rear seats have never been occupied. Mechanically, the car is flawless, with a complete service history documented exclusively through BMW authorized centers. Every forged wheel is free of curb rash, and the Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires have ample tread remaining. Included are both original keys, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
