    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total stunner. This car has been meticulously cared for and looks absolutely brand new\u2014not a scratch or smudge in sight! It\u2019s been garage-kept and babied since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
