    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S, featuring the venerable 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six. This specimen boasts a verified IMS bearing retrofit and has undergone a full borescope inspection to confirm zero cylinder wall scoring. The G97/01 6-speed manual transaxle shifts with surgical precision, exhibiting no synchro-drag or notchiness. The Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system is fully calibrated, retaining its factory damping rates for optimal lateral load transfer. The undercarriage is pristine, with all suspension kinematics\u2014including control arm bushings and drop links\u2014showing no signs of perishing or thermal fatigue. Braking is handled by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, providing fade-free deceleration with firm pedal modulation. This is a turn-key example for the collector demanding mechanical perfection and high-speed stability.",
